longBusinessSummary: Sarissa Resources Inc. engages in mineral exploration business in Canada. The company was formerly known as Michigan Mining Investment Inc. and changed its name to Sarissa Resources Inc. in December 2006. Sarissa Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Woodstock, Canada.
